      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "Wait, why the weird cookie and goblin analogies? I just need the actual math/logic for the optimization. Can you just stick to the algorithms like Nearest Neighbor or something? How would one of those actually work for my 12 stops?",
